{{!-- 12. Maʻruza va amaliy mashgʻulotlarining rejasi --}}
<h5>Maʻruza va amaliy mashgʻulotlarining rejasi</h5>
{{#if showInlineEdit}}
<div class="mb-3" data-inline-edit-panel data-refresh-url="{{urlPrefix}}/sillabuslar/{{sillabus.id}}/maruza-reja/fragment">{{> maruza_editable_table rows=maruzaRows nextNum=(increment maruzaRows.length)}}</div>
{{else}}
{{#if maruzaRows.length}}
<table style="width:100%; font-size:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <thead>
    <tr style="background:#f0f0f0;">
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:5%;">№</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:22%;">Mavzular</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:43%;">Dars mazmuni</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:10%;">Maʻruza soatlari hajmi</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:10%;">Amaliy mashgʻulot soatlari hajmi</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:10%;">Jami oʻquv soatlari hajmi</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each maruzaRows}}
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.tartib_raqam}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle;"><strong>{{this.mavzu}}</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px;">
        {{#if this.dars_mazmuni.length}}
        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:16px;">
          {{#each this.dars_mazmuni}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}
        </ul>
        {{else}}—{{/if}}
      </td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.maruza_soat}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.amaliy_soat}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{sum this.maruza_soat this.amaliy_soat}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr style="background:#f0f0f0; font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">Jami:</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">{{totalMaruza maruzaRows}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">{{totalAmaliy maruzaRows}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">{{totalJami maruzaRows}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
{{else}}
<p style="color:#999; text-align:center; margin-bottom:16px;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{!-- 13. Mustaqil taʻlim rejasi --}}
<h5>Mustaqil taʻlim mashgʻulotlari rejasi</h5>
{{#if showInlineEdit}}
<div class="mb-3" data-inline-edit-panel data-refresh-url="{{urlPrefix}}/sillabuslar/{{sillabus.id}}/mustaqil-talim/fragment">{{> mustaqil_editable_table rows=mustaqilRows nextNum=(increment mustaqilRows.length)}}</div>
{{else}}
{{#if mustaqilRows.length}}
<table style="width:100%; font-size:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <thead>
    <tr style="background:#f0f0f0;">
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:5%;"></th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:45%;">Mavzu</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:38%;">Topshiriq</th>
      <th style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; width:12%;">Soat</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each mustaqilRows}}
    <tr>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.tartib_raqam}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle;"><strong>{{this.mavzu}}</strong></td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px;">{{#if this.topshiriq}}{{#each (splitLetterItems this.topshiriq)}}<p style="margin:0;">{{this}}</p>{{/each}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.soat}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr style="background:#f0f0f0; font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">Jami</td>
      <td style="border:1px solid #333; padding:5px; text-align:center;">{{totalSoat mustaqilRows}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
{{else}}
<p style="color:#999; text-align:center; margin-bottom:16px;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{!-- 14-15. Fanni baholash mezoni (foiz) + Talabalar bilimini baholash mezoni (ball) --}}
<h5 style="margin-top:24px; margin-bottom:0;">FANNI BAHOLASH MEZONI VA REJASI</h5>
<p style="font-weight:bold; text-align:center; margin:0;">Talabalar bilimini baholash turlari.</p>
{{#if (eq sillabus.t_shakli "sirtqi")}}
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;">Mazkur fandan talabalar bilimini baholashda 2 ta nazorat turidan foydalaniladi. Joriy baholash (JB) va yakuniy imtihon (YI).</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>Joriy baholash (JB):</strong> Ushbu nazorat turi semestr davomida toʻplanib boriladi va quyidagilardan tarkib topadi:</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>Vazifa/topshiriqlar.</strong> Har bir talaba individual tarzda oʻqituvchi tomonidan berilgan vazifa/masala/topshiriqni bajaradi. Shuningdek, mustaqil taʻlim topshiriqlarini koʻrsatma boʻyicha bajaradi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin-bottom:6px;"><strong>Yakuniy imtihon (YI).</strong> Modulning oxirgi haftasida (25 yoki 50) test shaklida amalga oshiriladi.</p>
{{else}}
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;">Mazkur fandan talabalar bilimini baholashda joriy baholash (JB), oraliq imtihon (OI) va yakuniy imtihon (YI) turlaridan foydalaniladi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>Joriy baholash (JB):</strong> ushbu baholash turi 3 ta yoʻnalishda amalga oshiriladi:</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>1) Darsga qatnashish (DV)</strong>: talabaning dars mashgʻulotlariga kelishi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>2) Dars mashgʻulotlaridagi faollik</strong>: talabaning maʻruza va seminar mashgʻulotlaridagi faolligi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>3) Mustaqil taʻlim</strong>: Har bir talaba individual tarzda mustaqil taʻlim topshiriqlarini mazkur sillabusda qayd etilgan shakllarda bajaradi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin:0;"><strong>Oraliq imtihon (OI).</strong> Ushbu imtihon turi semestr davomida bir marta olinadi (8-haftada) fan (modul)ning oʻtilgan mavzulari asosida qisqa savol-javob yozma shaklda olinadi. Masofaviy taʻlim uchun oraliq imtihonlari test shaklida olinadi.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:2em; margin-bottom:6px;"><strong>Yakuniy imtihon (YI).</strong> Ushbu imtihon turi semestrning 16-haftasida (yakuniy imtihonlarga ajratilgan haftada) fan (modul)ning oʻtilgan barcha mavzulari doirasida yozma shaklda amalga oshiriladi. Masofaviy taʻlim uchun yakuniy imtihon test shaklida olinadi.</p>
{{/if}}
